(b) This section does not apply to a local law enforcement agency.
7-51-2803.
A jurisdiction that is affected by a violation of § 7-51-2801 or § 7-51-2802 may
seek damages and injunctive relief against the local governmental entity.
SECTION 2. This act takes effect upon becoming a law, the public welfare requiring it.
